# Frontend — Components Rules

Keep components **small and reusable**.

- Maximum component size: 200 lines
- One main responsibility per component
- Props: explicit types; required first, optional last
- Compose small components instead of large monolithic ones

Folder structure:

- `components/` — feature or layout components
- `ui/` or `components/ui/` — generic, reusable UI primitives
- `hooks/` — custom hooks
- `services/` — API clients and external calls
- `utils/` — pure helpers

Separate UI components from business logic.
